ISLAMABAD, Jan 20 (APP): Minister for Interior Sheikh Rashid Ahmed while condemning the blast at New Anarkali, Lahore, on Thursday sought a report from the Punjab Government into the incident.
The minister, in a statement, expressed deep sorrow and grief over the loss of precious lives in the blast. He also prayed for early recovery of the injured.
